d list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Custodian requirements High school diploma or equivalent Excellent time management skills in order to ensure all cleaning is completed by the end of each shift Knowledge of cleaning supplies and best practices Must be a self starter and take initiative by identifying opportunities to improve cleanliness Must be able to work with minimal supervision Ability to follow instructions carefully Custodian related job titles: Maintenance Clerk Janitorial Team Facility Maintenance Manager Overnight Janitor Janitor Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
